  <additional_information><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:my="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/infopath/2003/myXSD/2006-02-10T23:25:53">The LoadStyleFile method is used in the Form_Load event of the SymbolForm to add the contents of the ESRI.ServerStyle into the SymbologyControl. The StyleClass property is used to display text symbols in the SymbologyControl. When an item is selected by the end user from the SymbologyControl, a ServerStyleGalleryItem is returned.</div>
